    "The predictions of the LLMs compared to the ground truth for each label are presented in the confusion matrices in Figure 2B.",
    "The performance metrics are presented in Table 2 (RCT) and Table 3 (oncology).",
    "The classification task resulted in trials with correctly formatted predictions in 100% of abstracts with both models and labels for temperatures at or below 1.25.",
    "The biggest drop occurred again between temperatures 1.75 (98.9% for GPT-4o and 97.7% for GPT-4o mini) and 2.00 (93.3% for GPT-4o and 92.4% for GPT-4o mini) for both labels.",
    "The F1 scores for the label RCT ranged from 0.956 to 0.960 for GPT-4o and 0.914 to 0.921 for GPT-4o mini."
